        "Target": "\u30CC\u30B7\u30FB\u30A2\u30AA\u30A2\u30B7\u30E9\uFF11\u982D\u306E\u8A0E\u4F10",
        "Fail": "\u5831\u916C\u91D1\u30BC\u30ED\r\n\u30BF\u30A4\u30E0\u30A2\u30C3\u30D7"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Haste Makes Waste",
        "Client": "Hamon the Blacksmith",
        "Description": "Seems like power alone isn\u0027t\r\nenough these days\u2014hunters\r\nwant to look intelligent too. I\u0027d\r\ntake brawn over brains any day...\r\nI guess times are changing.\r\nComplete this request, and I\u0027ll\r\ngive you the required materials.",
        "Target": "Slay an Apex Arzuros",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Ouvrage h\u00E2t\u00E9, ouvrage g\u00E2t\u00E9",
        "Client": "Hamon le forgeron",
        "Description": "Comme quoi, la force ne suffit\r\nplus maintenant. Les chasseurs\r\nveulent aussi se creuser les\r\nm\u00E9ninges... Ah, la chasse\r\nn\u0027est plus ce qu\u0027elle \u00E9tait.\r\nOccupe-toi de ma requ\u00EAte et tu\r\nauras les mat\u00E9riaux requis.",
        "Target": "Tuer un Arzuros sup\u00E9rieur",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "La fretta \u00E8 cattiva consigliera",
        "Client": "Hamon il fabbro",
        "Description": "Oggigiorno il potere non basta:\r\ni cacciatori vogliono sembrare\r\nanche intelligenti. Io\r\npreferisco la forza al\r\ncervello... Ah, come cambiano\r\ni tempi! Completa la richiesta\r\ne ti dar\u00F2 i materiali necessari.",
        "Target": "Uccidi un Arzuros Apex",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Eile mit Weile",
        "Client": "Hamon der Schmied",
        "Description": "Heute reicht Kraft wohl nicht\r\nmehr, J\u00E4ger wollen intellektuell\r\nsein. Mir sind Muskeln lieber als\r\nKlugschei\u00DFerei... Die Zeiten\r\n\u00E4ndern sich. Erf\u00FClle meine\r\nAufgabe, dann geb ich dir die\r\nben\u00F6tigten Materialien.",
        "Target": "Erlege einen Apex-Arzuros.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Las cosas no son como eran",
        "Client": "Hamon el herrero",
        "Description": "A los cazadores de hoy en d\u00EDa\r\nno les basta con ser fuertes,\r\ntambi\u00E9n quieren parecer m\u00E1s\r\ninteligentes. Supongo que\r\nlos tiempos cambian. Te dar\u00E9\r\nlos materiales necesarios si\r\ncompletas esta misi\u00F3n.",
        "Target": "Abate un Arzuros Apex",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u041F\u043E\u0441\u043F\u0435\u0448\u0438\u0448\u044C \u2014 \u043B\u044E\u0434\u0435\u0439 \u043D\u0430\u0441\u043C\u0435\u0448\u0438\u0448\u044C",
